                        complete list of the United States Delegation see <hi rend="italic">Participation of the United States Government in International
                            Conferences, July 1, 1946–June 30, 1947</hi>, Department of State
                        Publication 3031 (Washington, Government Printing Office, 1948), p.
                        19.</note>
